{"type":"message","id":"93897354","parentId":"9cdedb47","timestamp":"2026-07-10T08:03:47.179Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ee38bf649563436990603a7a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/data/workspace/skills/linkedin-publish/li-post.sh \"264468965\" image \"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/fable5-outage-1783092385.png\" \"Your AI agent went down last week. You didn't notice.\n\nClaude Fable 5 went down for weeks. Only 1 in 10 enterprises had auto-failure detection.\n\nHere's the gap nobody's talking about.\n\nMost teams built their AI stack for happy paths:\n→ Model responds\n→ Agent completes task\n→ Everything works great\n\nBut what happens when the model goes down?\n\nSilent failures. Stuck workflows. Customers waiting. No alerts.\n\nThe enterprises that survived the outage had TWO things:\n1. Multi-model fallback (switch to GPT, Gemini, open-source)\n2. Health checks that actually ping the model — not just the API\n\nIf your monitoring says \\\"green\\\" but your agent is frozen, you don't have observability. You have a dashboard.\n\nThe real test: Can you detect a failure BEFORE your customers tell you?\n\nWhen did you last test your AI failure detection?\n\n#AI #AIAgents #Reliability #EnterpriseAI #Monitoring\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"/data/workspace/skills/linkedin-publish/li-post.sh \\\"264468965\\\" image \\\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/fable5-outage-1783092385.png\\\" \\\"Your AI agent went down last week. You didn't notice.\\n\\nClaude Fable 5 went down for weeks. Only 1 in 10 enterprises had auto-failure detection.\\n\\nHere's the gap nobody's talking about.\\n\\nMost teams built their AI stack for happy paths:\\n→ Model responds\\n→ Agent completes task\\n→ Everything works great\\n\\nBut what happens when the model goes down?\\n\\nSilent failures. Stuck workflows. Customers waiting. No alerts.\\n\\nThe enterprises that survived the outage had TWO things:\\n1. Multi-model fallback (switch to GPT, Gemini, open-source)\\n2. Health checks that actually ping the model — not just the API\\n\\nIf your monitoring says \\\\\\\"green\\\\\\\" but your agent is frozen, you don't have observability. You have a dashboard.\\n\\nThe real test: Can you detect a failure BEFORE your customers tell you?\\n\\nWhen did you last test your AI failure detection?\\n\\n#AI #AIAgents #Reliability #EnterpriseAI #Monitoring\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783670609024,"responseId":"UqdQasbIAsiGkuwP06bUqAY"}}
{"type":"message","id":"98f5e8dc","parentId":"93897354","timestamp":"2026-07-10T08:03:51.096Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ee38bf649563436990603a7a","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK: https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7481256860457787392/\nDISPLAY_NAME: Andrii Bidochko\nCHARS: 888"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3752,"aggregated":"OK: https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7481256860457787392/\nDISPLAY_NAME: Andrii Bidochko\nCHARS: 888","cwd":"/data/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783670631087}}
{"type":"message","id":"33d29732","parentId":"98f5e8dc","timestamp":"2026-07-10T08:04:00.858Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2cc3809e6f3c455987e0eae7","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Your AI agent went down last week. You didn't notice.\n\n**Published:** 2026-07-10T08:03:45Z\n**LinkedIn URL:** https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7481256860457787392/\n**Post URN:** urn:li:share:7481256860457787392\n**Format:** image\n**Characters:** 888\n**Pillar:** Technology & AI innovations\n**Image:** /data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/fable5-outage-1783092385.png\n\n## Post Body\n\nYour AI agent went down last week. You didn't notice.\n\nClaude Fable 5 went down for weeks. Only 1 in 10 enterprises had auto-failure detection.\n\nHere's the gap nobody's talking about.\n\nMost teams built their AI stack for happy paths:\n→ Model responds\n→ Agent completes task\n→ Everything works great\n\nBut what happens when the model goes down?\n\nSilent failures. Stuck workflows. Customers waiting. No alerts.\n\nThe enterprises that survived the outage had TWO things:\n1. Multi-model fallback (switch to GPT, Gemini, open-source)\n2. Health checks that actually ping the model — not just the API\n\nIf your monitoring says \"green\" but your agent is frozen, you don't have observability. You have a dashboard.\n\nThe real test: Can you detect a failure BEFORE your customers tell you?\n\nWhen did you last test your AI failure detection?\n\n#AI #AIAgents #Reliability #EnterpriseAI #Monitoring\n\n## Performance\n\n*(populated later by linkedin-analytics)*\n\n- **Impressions:** —\n- **Reactions:** —\n- **Comments:** —\n- **Shares:** —\n- **Last checked:** —\n","path":"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/posts/2026-07-10-your-ai-agent-went-down-last.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"content\": \"# Your AI agent went down last week. You didn't notice.\\n\\n**Published:** 2026-07-10T08:03:45Z\\n**LinkedIn URL:** https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7481256860457787392/\\n**Post URN:** urn:li:share:7481256860457787392\\n**Format:** image\\n**Characters:** 888\\n**Pillar:** Technology & AI innovations\\n**Image:** /data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/fable5-outage-1783092385.png\\n\\n## Post Body\\n\\nYour AI agent went down last week. You didn't notice.\\n\\nClaude Fable 5 went down for weeks. Only 1 in 10 enterprises had auto-failure detection.\\n\\nHere's the gap nobody's talking about.\\n\\nMost teams built their AI stack for happy paths:\\n→ Model responds\\n→ Agent completes task\\n→ Everything works great\\n\\nBut what happens when the model goes down?\\n\\nSilent failures. Stuck workflows. Customers waiting. No alerts.\\n\\nThe enterprises that survived the outage had TWO things:\\n1. Multi-model fallback (switch to GPT, Gemini, open-source)\\n2. Health checks that actually ping the model — not just the API\\n\\nIf your monitoring says \\\"green\\\" but your agent is frozen, you don't have observability. You have a dashboard.\\n\\nThe real test: Can you detect a failure BEFORE your customers tell you?\\n\\nWhen did you last test your AI failure detection?\\n\\n#AI #AIAgents #Reliability #EnterpriseAI #Monitoring\\n\\n## Performance\\n\\n*(populated later by linkedin-analytics)*\\n\\n- **Impressions:** —\\n- **Reactions:** —\\n- **Comments:** —\\n- **Shares:** —\\n- **Last checked:** —\\n\", \"path\": \"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/posts/2026-07-10-your-ai-agent-went-down-last.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fc5f5ad935b04a4f8a2ab3ef","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/pending/2026-07-10-draft-2.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/pending/2026-07-10-draft-2.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7888257beb5f427d9f181a54","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/pending/2026-07-10-draft-3.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/pending/2026-07-10-draft-3.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783670631111,"responseId":"aKdQarH-HKvx3PQPgd-yiAo"}}
